      <h2>Flights</h2>
      <p>Direct flights into Zaragoza (ZAZ) are limited. There’s one round-trip flight from London Stansted (STN) and one from Charleroi (CRL), both with Ryanair. Flights don’t operate every day of the week.</p>
      <p>Many more flights are available to Madrid, Barcelona, or Bilbao. These cities are around 3 hours’ drive from Zaragoza. Madrid and Barcelona have high-speed AVE trains to Zaragoza (about 1.5 hours).</p>
